<div class="container-fluid">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3 readyplay">
      <h4>Ready to Play?</h4>
      <br>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <p>Welcome <%= link_to "#{current_user.username}", edit_user_registration_path %>! Not you? <%= link_to 'Sign Out',  destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete  %></p><br/>
      
        Start a <%= link_to 'new game', new_game_path %> or <%= link_to 'join', games_path %> an existing match!
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-5 about-app">
      <h4>WHAT IS COUNTER THREAT?</h4>
      <br>
      <%= image_tag ("logo.png"), :class => 'img-responsive' %>
      <br>
      <p>Counter Threat Chess is a fullstack web application that allows users to play one another in fully-functional, live-updating games of chess. Gameplay is completely rule-enforced whether you're a beginner at chess or a grandmaster. Enjoy! </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 architects">
      <h4>The Architects of CounterThreat</h4>
      <br>
      <p><a href="www.kathleenfrench.co">Kathleen French</a> @<a href="https://www.github.com/frenchamnesty">github</a></p>
      <p>Haley Mnatzaganian @<a href="https://github.com/haleymnatz">github</a></p>
      <p>Lindsay Dages @<a href="https://github.com/lnzd17">github</a></p>
      <p>David Michael Pena @<a href="https://github.com/DavidMichaelPena">github</a></p>
      <p>Anna C @<a href="https://github.com/canelasa">github</a></p>
      <p>Mentored by: Abe Polishchuk</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
